Maanaadu (Tamil)

U/A 16+MovieActionSci-FiAdventure

Tamil

2021

Maanaadu is a cat and mouse race between the protagonist and the antagonist in a time loop where they try to beat each other out. When a certain condition is met, such as a death of a character, the loop starts again, where only the protagonist and the antagonist retain the memory of the previous loop and play a real mind game.

Audio Available in: Tamil
